description: Harvard has been an especially happy place since JoRochi’s hit the streets and began serving a heaping selection of refreshing Raspas: a deliciously sweet shaved ice treat. You’ll find all your favorite flavors; Tiger’s Blood, Margarita, Fuzzy Naple, Blue Raspberry, y mas! If you’re hungry, have yourself some nachos or a pretzel too! With all its fun and flavor, JaRochi’s Raspas y Mas is just the truck for you.
name: JaRochi's Raspas y Mas
